Name: Blue Barbarian Man
About the game: Help the blue barbarian man retrieve his special blue holy sword. you control the blue barbarian man who has the sword to hit his opponents. You can also jump on your enemies' heads to defeat them. You need to collect items and defeat bosses to finish the game. The game has 6 stages and two more secret stages.
